===Etymology===
Said to be from {{der|en|ny|lawi|malawi|flames}}, after the appearance of the sunrise over Lake Malawi; also possibly from '''[[Maravi]]''', the name of an early Malawi tribe, or from an old name for a lake. Chosen by {{w|Hastings Banda}} in 1964.

